IS opening an Investigation.

01:45.330 --> 01:47.469
Good.
There should be
an Investigation.

01:47.500 --> 01:49.206
Into what?
He's 17.

01:49.240 --> 01:52.869
By the state law
he is considered
to be an adult.

01:52.910 --> 01:54.798
Nova, he broke the law.

01:54.840 --> 01:57.502
Says the department
that depends on
trumped-up charges

01:57.550 --> 01:59.472
to keep the lights on.

02:01.750 --> 02:05.186
I wish every cop
was strong enough...

02:07.260 --> 02:09.683
to be as good a man
as you.

02:12.430 --> 02:15.729
My dad was a cop.

02:15.760 --> 02:18.866
His brother was a cop.

02:18.900 --> 02:21.289
My brother-in-law's a cop.

02:21.340 --> 02:25.231
I work with men and women
who are honorable.

02:25.270 --> 02:28.831
Cops with families
who pray that they come home
at the end of their days.

02:28.880 --> 02:32.611
Yeah, well, it's the same
prayer that black mothers
and fathers

02:32.650 --> 02:35.448
say to the children
every time they walk
out of the house

02:35.480 --> 02:37.641
for over 300 years.

